{c_label}Lucky Hit:{/c} {c_important}Eagle{/c} Skills have up to a {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} chance to spawn a {c_important}{u}Storm Feather{/u}{/c} at your target. 

Each {c_important}{u}Storm Feather{/u}{/c} you pick up now also reduces your {c_important}Mobility{/c} Skill Cooldowns by {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0" * (1+Owner.Bonus_Percent_Per_Power#Spiritborn_Feather_Spawn)|1|]{/c} seconds.
